T*(me: and mind, particularly, to notice that the sexton obeys my directions)Tj
T*(concerning the two coffins!  No minister need come; nor need anything be)Tj
T*(said over me.--I tell you I have nearly attained _my_ heaven; and that of)Tj
T*(others is altogether unvalued and uncovered by me.')Tj
